  <h1>Docs.</h1>

  <%# ---------- THE LOUD CALLOUT ---------- %>
  <aside class="agent-notice">
    <span class="meta-label">Heads up. For humans.</span>
    <h2>These docs are for <em>you</em>, not your agent.</h2>
    <p>
      Your AI assistant doesn't need to read this. Just paste your MCP connector URL into
